column1: Name (Company Name as registered on stock exchanges)
column2: BSE Code (Ticker symbol on Bombay Stock Exchange)
column3: NSE Code (Ticker symbol on National Stock Exchange of India)
column4: Industry (Sector or industry classification of the company)
column5: Current Price (Latest market price per share in INR)
column6: Price to Earning (Price-to-Earnings ratio: current price divided by annual earnings per share)
column7: Market Capitalization (Total market value of outstanding shares in INR)
column8: Earnings yield (Annual earnings per share divided by current share price; inverse of P/E ratio)
column9: Div plus Earning Yield (Sum of dividend yield and earnings yield; combined annual yield to shareholder)
column10: CROIC (Cash Return on Invested Capital: how much operating cash flow is generated per rupee invested)
column11: Return on assets (Net income divided by average total assets; measures asset efficiency)
column12: PEG Ratio (Price/Earnings to Growth ratio: P/E divided by annual EPS growth rate)
column13: NPM last year (Net Profit Margin for the most recent fiscal year)
column14: Change in promoter holding 3Years (Three-year change in percentage points of promoter shareholding)
column15: Sales growth 3Years (Three-year compound annual growth rate of sales revenue)
column16: EPS growth 3Years (Three-year compound annual growth rate of earnings per share)
column17: Debt to equity (Total debt divided by shareholders’ equity; measure of financial leverage)
column18: Dividend yield (Annual dividend per share divided by current price; income return percentage)
column19: Dividend Payout Ratio (Percentage of net income distributed as dividends)
column20: Price to book value (Market price divided by book value per share; valuation metric)
column21: Pledged percentage (Percentage of promoter shares pledged as loan collateral)
column22: EPS growth 10Years (Ten-year compound annual growth rate of earnings per share)
column23: Return over 1year (Total shareholder return—including dividends—over past 1 year)
column24: Return over 10years (Total shareholder return—including dividends—over past 10 years)
column25: Return on capital employed (Return on capital employed: EBIT divided by (total assets – current liabilities))
column26: Price to Free Cash Flow (Market cap divided by free cash flow; valuation relative to cash generation)
column27: Price to Sales (Market capitalization divided by total revenue; valuation metric)
column28: FCF to EBIT (Free cash flow divided by earnings before interest & taxes; cash conversion efficiency)
column29: FCF to NW (Free cash flow divided by net worth; return metric on equity)
column30: FCF by OpCF (Free cash flow as a percentage of operating cash flow; cash conversion ratio)
column31: Sales (Total revenue for the most recent reported period)
column32: OPM (Operating Profit Margin: operating income divided by sales)
column33: Profit after tax (Net income for the most recent reported period)
column34: Sales latest quarter (Revenue during the most recent fiscal quarter)
column35: Profit after tax latest quarter (Net income during the most recent fiscal quarter)
column36: YOY Quarterly sales growth (Year-on-year percentage change in quarterly sales)
column37: YOY Quarterly profit growth (Year-on-year percentage change in quarterly net income)
column38: Return on equity (Net income divided by shareholders’ equity; return on investor capital)
column39: EPS (Earnings per share for the most recent reported period)
column40: Debt (Total outstanding debt, both short- and long-term)
column41: Promoter holding (Current percentage of total shares held by promoters)
column42: Change in promoter holding (Recent change in promoter holding percentage; time period unclear)
column43: Industry PE (Average Price/Earnings ratio for the company's industry)
column44: Sales growth (Growth rate of sales over unspecified period; likely year-over-year)
column45: Profit growth (Growth rate of profit over unspecified period; likely year-over-year)
column46: EVEBITDA (Enterprise Value divided by EBITDA; valuation multiple)
column47: Enterprise Value (Market cap plus debt minus cash; total firm value)
column48: Current ratio (Current assets divided by current liabilities; measure of liquidity)
column49: Interest Coverage Ratio (EBIT or operating income divided by interest expense; ability to service debt)
column50: Return over 3months (Total shareholder return—including dividends—over past 3 months)
column51: Return over 6months (Total shareholder return—including dividends—over past 6 months)
column52: Sales growth 5Years (Five-year compound annual growth rate of sales)
column53: Profit growth 3Years (Three-year compound annual growth rate of net profit)
column54: Profit growth 5Years (Five-year compound annual growth rate of net profit)
column55: Average return on equity 5Years (Arithmetic average ROE over past 5 years)
column56: Average return on equity 3Years (Arithmetic average ROE over past 3 years)
column57: Return over 3years (Total shareholder return—including dividends—over past 3 years)
column58: Return over 5years (Total shareholder return—including dividends—over past 5 years)
column59: Sales last year (Total revenue in the previous fiscal year)
